{
  "stem": "3757.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the 16th of October, at the evening, like-- like a miracle, Irene appeared.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She-- well, in the-- in the town where-- where she lived, already the Russian came in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was escaping through forests and ditches and I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were bombing and everything above her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she had that feeling, she has to come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She has to help us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she arrived on the 16th.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She really, really risk her life a few times for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so I went down to the super.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I told, let-- let Irene out with the child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "No way, no way, no way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I promised him money and more money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No, he cannot do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But his wife was always envy of the beautiful carriage what I had for my son and the clothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I go to give them to her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I told Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Braun, ?] convince your husband to let out only.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You are a mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You understand.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I wanted Irene takes [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I will give you a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And you can go up to my apartment and to take whatever you want to-- all the clothes of [HUNGARIAN], the carriage, everything what you want to.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she convinced him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I had a small clutch pocketbook.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had money in it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I had Irene's paper, too, and money to give to the-- to this man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he opened the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was pitch dark outside because was blackout.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when he opened the-- the entrance gate, I jumped after Irene went out with the-- with the child.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I jumped out, without a coat, without anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I thought, now where do we go?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
